[{},{"attrs":{"title":"Now Deployment","description":"How to deploy Nuxt.js app with Now?"},"body":"<h1><a id=\"how-to-deploy-with-now-\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#how-to-deploy-with-now-\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>How to deploy with Now?</h1><h2><a id=\"now-v2\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#now-v2\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Now V2</h2><p><strong>Note:</strong> You cannot deploy a server-side-rendered Nuxt app with Now V2 right now. Please use Now V1 for such apps.</p>\n<p>To deploy with <a href=\"https://zeit.co/now\">ZEIT Now</a> you need to customize <code>package.json</code> add create a <code>now.json</code> config.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add <code>now-build</code> script command to <code>package.json</code>:<ul>\n<li>For SPA (without SSR):<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scripts\"</span>: {\n   ...\n   <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"now-build\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"nuxt build --spa\"</span>\n}</code></pre></li>\n<li>For Static Generated (Pre Rendering):<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scripts\"</span>: {\n   ...\n   <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"now-build\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"nuxt generate\"</span>\n}</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Create <code>now.json</code> and define <code>builds</code><pre><code class=\"hljs json\">{\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"version\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"builds\"</span>: [\n    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"src\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"package.json\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"use\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"@now/static-build\"</span> }\n  ]\n}</code></pre></li>\n<li>Run <code>now</code> and enjoy!</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a id=\"now-v1-legacy-\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#now-v1-legacy-\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Now V1 (legacy)</h2><p>To deploy with <a href=\"https://zeit.co/now\">now.sh</a> a <code>package.json</code> like follows is recommended:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs json\">{\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"name\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"my-app\"</span>,\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"dependencies\"</span>: {\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"nuxt\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"latest\"</span>\n  },\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"scripts\"</span>: {\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"dev\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"nuxt\"</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"build\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"nuxt build\"</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"start\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"nuxt start\"</span>\n  }\n}</code></pre><p>Then run <code>now</code> and enjoy!</p>\n<p>Note: we recommend putting <code>.nuxt</code> in <code>.npmignore</code> or <code>.gitignore</code>.</p>\n","docLink":"https://github.com/nuxt/docs/blob/master/en/faq/now-deployment.md"}]